	id = smm.1063

		name = smm_1061_o9
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = {

			}

			}

				value = 0.001
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_9
				which = smm_colors
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_9
				which = smm_scale
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_9
				which = smm_res
			}
			change_variable = {

country_event = { 
	id = smm.1065
	title = "smm_999_t"
	desc = "smm_1065_d"
	picture = MEIOU_AND_TAXES_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = smm_1061_o17
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_17
				value = 0
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_colors
				value = 100000
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_scale
				value = 1000
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_res
				value = 100
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_type
				value = 0.001
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_17
				which = smm_colors
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_17
				which = smm_scale
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_17
				which = smm_res
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_17
				which = smm_scope
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_17
				which = smm_type
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_colors
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scale
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_res
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scope
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_type
				value = 0
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = smm_rev
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = smm_custom_slot_17
					value = -1
				}
				clr_country_flag = smm_rev
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_colors_1
				which = smm_colors
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scale_1
				which = smm_scale
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_res_1
				which = smm_res
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scope_1
				which = smm_scope
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_type_1
				which = smm_type
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = smm_rev
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							has_country_flag = smm_rev_1
						}
					}
					set_country_flag = smm_rev_1
				}
			}
			else = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = smm_rev_1
					}
					clr_country_flag = smm_rev_1
				}
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = smm_no_slot_1
				}
				clr_country_flag = smm_no_slot_1
			}
			country_event = { 
				id = smm.1064
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = smm_1061_o18
		hidden_effect = {

				which = smm_type
				value = 0
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = smm_rev

				multiply_variable = { 
					which = smm_custom_slot_18

				}
				clr_country_flag = smm_rev

country_event = { 
	id = smm.1067
	title = "smm_999_t"
	desc = "smm_1067_d"
	picture = MEIOU_AND_TAXES_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = smm_1061_o25
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_25
				value = 0
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_colors
				value = 100000
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_scale
				value = 1000
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_res
				value = 100
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = smm_type
				value = 0.001
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_25
				which = smm_colors
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_25
				which = smm_scale
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_25
				which = smm_res
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_25
				which = smm_scope
			}
			change_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_25
				which = smm_type
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_colors
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scale
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_res
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scope
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_type
				value = 0
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = smm_rev
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = smm_custom_slot_25
					value = -1
				}
				clr_country_flag = smm_rev
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_colors_1
				which = smm_colors
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scale_1
				which = smm_scale
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_res_1
				which = smm_res
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_scope_1
				which = smm_scope
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_type_1
				which = smm_type
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = smm_rev
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						NOT = { 
							has_country_flag = smm_rev_1
						}
					}
					set_country_flag = smm_rev_1
				}
			}
			else = { 
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						has_country_flag = smm_rev_1
					}
					clr_country_flag = smm_rev_1
				}
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					has_country_flag = smm_no_slot_1
				}
				clr_country_flag = smm_no_slot_1
			}
			country_event = { 
				id = smm.1066
			}
		}
	}

	option = { 
		name = smm_1061_o33
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = smm_custom_slot_33
				value = 0
			}

				which = smm_colors

			}

				which = smm_res

		name = SMMResNameOpt1

				}

				}
